data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER is offering a $4000 allowance with an acceptable offer!!  
Charming home in Tanglewood subdivision sitting on a nice corner lot. This home features three bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, formal living and dining room for all your extra company, den/family room has a nice wood burning fireplace and for the cook, you will love entertaining in this kitchen with gorgeous granite countertops and open to breakfast area, built-in desk. And if that's not enough, a third living space perfect for the recreation, workout, playroom, study or how ever you can best utilize it. Large laundry room and so much more. Oh and there is room for the boat or RV! Home had foundation repairs done in 2016. No issues since. The Lifetime Warranty is transferrable.
